  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400 F (200 C).",
    "Lightly oil a baking sheet with olive oil.",
    "Pat bonito fillets dry with paper towels.",
    "Season fillets with kabse spice, salt, and pepper.",
    "Arrange fillets on baking sheet, skin side up.",
    "Place lemon slices and rosemary sprigs between fillets.",
    "Roast fillets for 10 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "While roasting, heat balsamic glaze in a small saucepan until slightly thickened.",
    "Remove fillets from oven and drizzle glaze evenly over each fillet.",
    "Sprinkle minced garlic over the fillets and return to oven for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Transfer fillets to plates, add pomegranate seeds as garnish if desired.",
    "Serve immediately with a side of roasted vegetables or couscous."
  ],
